{"tid":770632,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 李嘉欣孖老公出遊忽然手袋護肚仔","createTime":"2018-08-07T09:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T09:57:03.000Z","uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"975613f5f463e82ed6c3b6273996f8c00beccc30","tid":770632,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:15:18.000Z","msg":"大美人李嘉欣（Michele）同老公許晉亨結婚十年，依然恩愛如昔，近日兩公婆仲去咗美國三藩市旅行，Michele喺社交網上載喺街頭同老公影嘅合照，留言話：「難得放風」網民估計兩人今次冇同仔仔Jayden同行，純粹過二人世界，所以先形容自己係放風。 <br />\n<br />\n相中嘅Michele同老公十指緊扣，而且步伐一致，Michele又將個手袋仔擺喺肚皮位置遮肚，加埋用手護肚嘅動作，有網民就好敏感猜測Michele係咪&hellip;&hellip;有喜？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/07/171516_c3048c77eece2de24dbb8d28f9d163ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F07%2F171516_c3048c77eece2de24dbb8d28f9d163ec.png&h=25cd00bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9986c371bf7ad63baf2f258299c347bcd889075","tid":770632,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:15:55.000Z","msg":"​​​​<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif&h=74a0e790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/135859_8ef13172083af6d92739df9095300d9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F135859_8ef13172083af6d92739df9095300d9b.jpg&h=02ebf494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/135910_de6dd01ad3a6bdafd0dfa526dfeb4aad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F135910_de6dd01ad3a6bdafd0dfa526dfeb4aad.jpg&h=f9ef9f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload